Class Feed

java.lang.Object
  com.vtls.opensource.rss.Feed
Direct Known Subclasses:
RSSFeed
public abstract class Feed
extends Object

A base class for our Feed implementations. We'd like to keep the feed format (RSS, Atom) separate from the model.
